 (493.90), <a href="/web/20180713050647/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0302378&amp;fLockTerm=Chronic+airway+obstruction%2c+not+elsewhere+classified">Chronic airway obstruction, not elsewhere classified</a>
 (496), <a href="/web/20180713050647/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0155866&amp;fLockTerm=Pneumonia+in+anthrax">Pneumonia in anthrax</a>
 (022.1), <a href="/web/20180713050647/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0155866&amp;fLockTerm=Pneumonia+in+anthrax">Pneumonia in anthrax</a>
