                <h2 id="420" class="accordion-title section-420 is-active" role="tab" aria-expanded="true"><a href="#">Recommendations</a></h2>
            <div class="accordion-panel is-active" role="tabpanel">
                        <h3><a href="#">Major Recommendations</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p><strong>ACR Appropriateness Criteria&reg;</strong></p>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Clinical Condition</span>: Acute Respiratory Illness in Immunocompetent Patients</strong></p>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Variant 1:</span> Older than age 40.</strong></p>
<table border="1" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="5" summary="Table: Variant 1: Acute Respiratory Illness in Immunocompetent Patients. Older than age 40">
